    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AdjacencyDetector
    The AdjacencyDetector class is responsible for detecting adjacent properties based on their polygon coordinates.
    AdjacentPropertyPair
    The AdjacentPropertyPair class represents a pair of adjacent properties identified by their IDs.
    ChangeSuggestionsFrame
    The ChangeSuggestionsFrame class represents a JFrame that displays suggested changes for property exchanges based on adjacent properties.
    CoordinateFinder
    The CoordinateFinder class provides utility methods to find the maximum and minimum X and Y coordinates from a list of PropertyPolygon objects.
    CsvColum
    The CsvColum enum represents the columns in a CSV file related to geographical data.
    CsvException
    The CsvColum enum represents the columns in a CSV file related to geographical data.
    CsvLogger
    The CsvLogger class provides methods to log messages to a CSV file.
    CsvProcessor
    The CsvProcessor class processes CSV data related to geographical regions, municipalities, and parishes.
    CsvReader
    The CsvReader class provides methods to read CSV files.
    CsvUploader
    The CsvUploader class provides methods to upload and read CSV files.
    CsvValidator
    The CsvValidator class provides methods to validate the contents of a CSV file.
    CyclomaticComplexity
    The CyclomaticComplexity annotation is used to specify the cyclomatic complexity of a method.
    District
    The District class represents a district within a municipality.
    ExchangeSuggestion
    The ExchangeSuggestion class represents a suggestion for an exchange between two properties.
    GraphViewer
    The GraphViewer class provides utility methods to visualize a graph of PropertyPolygon nodes using the JUNG library.
    Layer
    The Layer annotation is used to specify the layer type of a class.
    LayerType
    The LayerType enum represents the different layers of an application.
    LoadingDialogSpinner
    The LoadingDialogSpinner class represents a modal dialog that displays a loading spinner and a message while a process is running.
    MainFrame
    The MainFrame class represents the main graphical user interface (GUI) of the application.
    MaxCoordinateFinder
    Deprecated.
    This class is deprecated and will be removed in a future release.
    MinCoordinateFinder
    Deprecated.
    This class is deprecated and will be removed in a future release.
    MockedDistrict
    The MockedDistrict class is a mock implementation of the District class.
    MockedMunicipality
    The MockedMunicipality class is a mock implementation of the Municipality class.
    MockedParish
    The MockedParish class is a mock implementation of the Parish class.
    MockedPropertyPolygon
    The MockedPropertyPolygon class is a mock implementation of the PropertyPolygon class.
    Municipality
    The Municipality class represents a municipality within a district.
    Parish
    The Parish class represents a parish within a municipality.
    Polygon
    The Polygon class represents a geometric shape defined by a list of vertices.
    PropertyCollector
    The PropertyCollector class is responsible for collecting and filtering property data from a list of districts.
    PropertyGraphJungBuilder
    The PropertyGraphJungBuilder class is responsible for building a graph representation of property polygons using the JUNG library.
    PropertyInfoDialog
    The PropertyInfoDialog class is a custom dialog that displays detailed information about a specific property.
    PropertyMerger
    The PropertyMerger class provides functionality to merge adjacent properties with the same owner into unified properties.
    PropertyOwnership
    Deprecated.
    PropertyPolygon
    The PropertyPolygon class represents a property with a polygonal shape.
    PropertyScoreCalculator
    The PropertyScoreCalculator class is responsible for assigning tourism and urbanization scores to municipalities and parishes based on the number of properties and monuments in each region.
    Region
    The Region interface represents a geographical region with a name.
    SuggestionGenerator
    The SuggestionGenerator class is responsible for generating exchange suggestions between adjacent properties based on their owners and areas.
    TestUtils
    Utility class providing helper methods for creating test data and graphs used in unit tests for the DetectAdjacentProperties package.
    TestUtils
    Utility class providing helper methods for creating test data and graphs used in unit tests for the Services package.
    VertexCoordinate
    The VertexCoordinate record represents a vertex in a 2D space with X and Y coordinates.
